messages.message:
X-posting the numbers that @Kerry referred to during the All Hands about comparing AI Hub to the competition :fire:
> We produced recently some data to compare our retrieval with another product that offers similar features (pdf.ai (http://pdf.ai))
> Looks like we are doing quite well - we compared our app with pdf.ai (http://pdf.ai) answers on >100 long-document questions we have in the benchmark
> 
> *Here are the scores*
> • pdf.ai (http://pdf.ai) - *0.58*
> • AI HUB gpt-3.5-turbo - *0.77*
> • AI HUB gpt-4 - *0.85*
> we also have a version (not yet merged as we need more tests) with the below scores
> • AI HUB gpt-3.5-turbo - *0.84*
> • AI HUB gpt-4 - *0.87*
>
